      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Explorative analyses: Multivariate Cox regression analyses of DFS and OS. Evaluate the prognostic value of patterns of PET positivity using the Akaike information criterion (AIC) and using indexes of the proportion of variation explained by covariates.",
